title: 2019 Week 3 Recap
itunes:title: 2019 Week 3 Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap every game of week 3 including the highly anticipated Ravens Chiefs game (02:23), Matt "the flowers" third win in a row (23:24) and the beginning of the Daniel Jones era. (44:18). Oh, sunday night sad emoji. (1:15:28)
